lead_paragraph: Nothing was routine for Bud Norris in his first start for the Dodgers. New time zone. New uniform. Being penciled into Clayton Kershaw's place in the Los Angeles rotation.

headline.print_headline: Norris Fills In for Kershaw as Dodgers Beat Rockies 5-0
